性，让民主党人永远掌权，摧毁我们的宪法”。 据复旦发展研究院发表的分析文章称，《为人民法案》是一个降低选举权门槛的法案。因为固有的选举流程过于繁琐，导致低收入街区和少数族裔投票率太低。这项法案是由民主党提出的，而在众议院针对该法案的投票表决中，209位出席的共和党议员都投了反对票。 此外，公开信还质疑美国总统拜登的身心健康状况。信中称，“这位统帅的身心健康状况不容忽视。他必须能够无论白天黑夜，能在任何地方快速、准确地作出涉及国家安全问题的决策”、“我们必须得拥有无可置疑的指挥系统”。 但据《商业内幕》（Business Insider）报道称，在本月早些时候，拜登的医师凯文·奥康纳(Kevin O'Connor)发布了一份有关拜登健康状况的报告，报告中称拜登“健康、充满活力”、“能够胜任总统一职”。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I7MDj7v62ufZZEAMaCDY0MzgzODM0IKGL+oQGMAo4ogNAA3IJNDU5NDY2MDg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"580 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-c00d06683a44d26d35da512ecbc99564_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1621052044.2507195","card_id":"Q_32090742","target":{"id":32090742,"title":"《盗墓笔记》讲了什么?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/32090742","type":"question","created":1436537164,"answer_count":51,"follower_count":1056,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6878,8048,21035,25613,27867],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"盗墓笔记看完了，但是很混乱，而且忘了很多细节。。。"},"attached_info":"Cj0I7MDj7v62ufZZEAMaBzUwMzU2MTcgzKL/rAUwATigCEAEcggzMjA5MDc0MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"473 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-bb1834f904e3290da123e7ea0e4c419c_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"5_1621052044.2512717","card_id":"Q_319597687","target":{"id":319597687,"title":"跟大叔谈恋爱什么感觉？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/319597687","type":"question","created":1554905626,"answer_count":544,"follower_count":3064,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4729,8451,141361],"comment_count":44,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"跟大叔谈恋爱真的那么甜吗？"},"attached_info":"Cj8I7